{"tid":1065982,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"問男朋友鐘意我啲咩","createTime":"2019-03-17T15:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T22:29:41.000Z","uid":66441,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"de87b99e1ea47972a2cf71d1b6734964ec1859f9","tid":1065982,"uid":66441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:46:16.000Z","msg":"佢話鐘意我獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以你就成日唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n我唔獨立嫁屌好想無時無刻都搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實佢係真誠地覺得獨立係好事 定係有可藉口對我愛理不理？抑或其實佢唔係咁鐘意我？<br />\n男仔如果真係好鐘意個女朋友係咪應該成日都好想見佢，唔會話覺得見少啲係好事，或者女朋友可以唔駛點理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n由於佢成日唔理我我依家都少搵佢了<br />\n變到好似真係好獨立咁，但其實係抑壓緊自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5fe556a3aa8ec17097bc5be0ed481ae0e1bb087","tid":1065982,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:46:31.000Z","msg":"有仔就收皮啦"},{"pid":"7d7cd1b3e86f08d6cf95170ad8aa4f0374e857fa","tid":1065982,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de6e78a31f4974330c94478108fc28c1e81d5e6","tid":1065982,"uid":224453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:47:26.000Z","msg":"我可以做你後備男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9477e2c6a502853cebc3fcf2fa5143cb0799e01","tid":1065982,"uid":431,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"鍾意你lemon stealing whore"},{"pid":"a05af0ff07bb3670ae7ca27d9ca2986d39ca4787","tid":1065982,"uid":183853,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:52:33.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過同佢傾下 自己估估下<br />\n然後佢又當你真係獨立 互相又少搵大家都幾影響感情"},{"pid":"33d5b53e1f8107db5faa60fd323c6ee6b35aa250","tid":1065